# Push-based extraction pipeline (Karpathy LLM Wiki).
#
# Política 2026-05-02 (opción B):
#   - Per-video JSONs (<video_id>.json) y snapshots de prompt → gitignored
#     (intermedios voluminosos, derivables del corpus + scope.md histórico)
#   - applied_backup/ → gitignored (pre-edit copies, redundantes con git history)
#   - state.json → gitignored (control efímero de progreso)
#   - Aggregator outputs (discard_log, pending_updates, promote_queue,
#     thesis_candidates, blocks_filtered, aggregation_stats) → COMMITED
#   - applied_log.json → COMMITED (audit trail de cada apply)
wiki/_meta/extraction_runs/*
!wiki/_meta/extraction_runs/*/
wiki/_meta/extraction_runs/*/*
!wiki/_meta/extraction_runs/*/discard_log.json
!wiki/_meta/extraction_runs/*/pending_updates.json
!wiki/_meta/extraction_runs/*/promote_queue.json
!wiki/_meta/extraction_runs/*/thesis_candidates.json
!wiki/_meta/extraction_runs/*/blocks_filtered.json
!wiki/_meta/extraction_runs/*/aggregation_stats.json
!wiki/_meta/extraction_runs/*/applied_log.json
wiki/_meta/extraction_runs/*/applied_backup/
